Package: lsmsrprojtempl2
Title: Rstudio/R project set-up for LSMS style shiny application with
    modules
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Michael", "Wild", , "mwild@worldbank.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package is intended to be used as a project template for
    RStudio projects, when creating LSMS style special purpose
    applications (SPA) by using R's Shiny framework as R packages.  It
    includes basic styles and functions to create a SPA with modules.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports:
    formatR,
    usethis,
    utils,
    rlang
Encoding: UTF-8
Language: en
